The '''akorec''' was a vicious, [[Reptile/Legends|reptilian]] creature native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Trammis III/Legends|Trammis III]]. An average akorec stood at around ten [[Meter/Legends|meters]] tall at the shoulder and had a long head with a mouth filled with huge [[Tooth/Legends|teeth]].

The akorec was a feared predator, not least because its scales were resistant to [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]]-fire. The [[Scillal Designs]] [[891c Akorec-class strike cruiser|891c ''Akorec''-class strike cruiser]] was named after this creature.

